Start Apache and MySQL in XAMPP.

Use Postman to Test Requests

GET Tasks
Method: GET
URL: http://localhost/api.php
Headers: API_KEY: 1234567890abcdef

Create Task
Method: POST
URL: http://localhost/api.php
Headers: API_KEY: 1234567890abcdef
Body (JSON):

json :
{
  "title": "New Task",
  "description": "This is a new task."
}
Update Task
Method: PUT
URL: http://localhost/api.php
Headers: API_KEY: 1234567890abcdef
Body (JSON):

json:
{
  "id": 1,
  "title": "Updated Task",
  "description": "This task has been updated."
}

Delete Task
Method: DELETE
URL: http://localhost/api.php
Headers: API_KEY: 1234567890abcdef
Body (JSON):

json{
  "id": 1
}
